data.title: Download Free PDF
data.meta_description: GK Handbook - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides information about general knowledge (GK) and its importance for various MBA entrance exams such as CMAT, SNAP, IIFT, and others. It discusses how GK can be categorized into static, current, and business-related areas. It then provides details on preparing for the GK sections, including recommended study methods and resources. Sample GK questions are also included related to topics like SAARC countries, highways in India, and Nobel Prizes.
